snippet.title: FreeJack Gameplay Trailer (Parkour Game)
snippet.description:
http://www.freemmogamer.com/2010/01/freejack.html for FreeJack, overview, videos, screenshots and more. FreeJack is a free-to-play parkour racing game for Windows PCs. Players race head-to-head across the urban metropolis of New Jack City as one of four hip characters, bustin' stylish flips and tricks to increase their speed and gain access to hidden pathways and shortcuts.

http://www.freemmogamer.com for all free to play MMORPGs and MMO Games.
